room_title: Escape room "Curse of the Undead" by Epic Escape Game in Cheyenne
room_description:
A deadly virus named the "Curse" has spread throughout the world turning its victims into the undead. It has been rumored that Dr. Leon Gordis, a leading scientist from the Bio EPID Lab has developed a cure. He is now missing.
You and your team from the CDC (Center for Disease Control) have been sent to Dr. Gordis' lab to find the cure...if it even exists. During your search, the undead has descended upon the lab. Now it's up to you to reverse the Curse of the undead, escape the lab and save the world before it's too late.
